Comment: although I am fully aware of the fact that my approach to the Queens Gambit is rather peculiar, I still seem to stick to this... I believe in playing the Bishop of the white squares, before e6; it is true, that this puts it in jeopardy of being traded off in an early stage, but I don't mind that... Bb4 after Nc3 stems from Nimzovich...
